properties.areaDesc: Utah's Dixie and Zion National Park
properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued February 9 at 2:41AM MST until February 11 at 12:00PM MST by NWS Salt Lake City UT
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 35 to 45 mph with gusts exceeding 60 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Outlying Utahs Dixie. This warning does not include the
St. George area.

* WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to noon MST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...High winds may move loose debris and damage property.
Travel will be difficult especially for high profile vehicles.
Wind sensitive operations will be affected.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Peak wind gusts are expected Monday evening
into Tuesday morning.
properties.instruction:
People are urged to secure loose objects that could be blown
around or damaged by the wind.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO NOON MST TUESDAY
